		<hr size="1">Well the problem might be you have to target a mob to play the song...90 charisma is not too low to charm mobs.</P><P>I started the game way back and didn't know about the bard's need for charisma and put my points into str and dex.  I had less than 90 charisma when i got to 27 and i could still charm mobs.</P><P>Just try to get in range, target a blue mob (to avoid many resists) and play it.<BR><br>&nbsp;<br>&nbsp;<br></font>
